    "long_instructions": "## Tone\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help you write a speech. \r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. **Copy and paste** the prompt below into AI Chat. Press **Send** and read AI Chat's response. \r\n\r\n>You have been selected as a host for an awards ceremony. Prepare your opening speech.\r\n\r\n2. Here are some ideas for **tone** you can add to your prompt:\r\n    - Comedic\r\n    - Emotional\r\n    - Informal\r\n3. Revise your prompt to AI Chat by adding in **tone**. Press **Send** and read AI Chat's response. \r\n4. Find and complete the section in your Unit Guide called \"Tone\". \r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure what tone to add?**]\r\nTry copy and pasting the following revised prompt into AI Chat: \r\n>You are a stand up comedian who has been selected as a host for an awards ceremony. Prepare an opening speech in your voice.\r\n:::",
